 </code><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>Amends the Criminal Code of 2012.  Provides that the sentence for </code><code>aggravated criminal sexual assault, which does not otherwise provide for an </code><code>enhanced penalty, is a Class X felony for which 5 years shall
be added to </code><code>the term of imprisonment imposed by the court.  Provides that  the sentence </code><code>for  predatory criminal sexual assault of a child, which does not otherwise </code><code>provide for an enhanced penalty,  is a Class X felony with a minimum term of </code><code>imprisonment of 11 (rather than 6) years.</code><code>
